## Getting Started

### Install dependencies

{{#if buildTool}}
{{#eq buildTool "uv"}}
```bash
uv sync
```
{{/eq}}
{{#eq buildTool "poetry"}}
```bash
poetry install
```
{{/eq}}
{{else}}
```bash
uv sync
# or
poetry install
```
{{/if}}

### Run the service

{{#if buildTool}}
{{#eq buildTool "uv"}}
```bash
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```
{{/eq}}
{{#eq buildTool "poetry"}}
```bash
poetry run uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```
{{/eq}}
{{else}}
```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```
{{/if}}

### Run tests

```bash
pytest
```

## API Endpoints

- `GET /health` - Health check
- `GET /api/v1/hello` - Example endpoint
{{#if enableSwagger}}
- `GET /docs` - Swagger UI
- `GET /redoc` - ReDoc
{{/if}}
{{#if enableMetrics}}
- `GET /metrics` - Prometheus metrics
{{/if}}

## Configuration

Environment variables:
- `PORT` - Server port (default: 8000)
- `LOG_LEVEL` - Logging level (default: info)

## Docker

Build image:
```bash
docker build -t {{projectName}} .
```

Run container:
```bash
docker run -p 8000:8000 {{projectName}}
```

